{"tid":2429550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拜登揚言有方法令中國遵守國際規則及保障人權","createTime":"2021-03-02T11:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T01:32:14.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"bdcef60d14fc4912cbb94a509a768bf58c55b4b6","tid":2429550,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:32:55.000Z","msg":"辯論中多次提及中國，拜登揚言一旦當選，會迫使中國遵守國際規則。至於曾表示中國要為新冠病毒疫情付出代價的特朗普，則未有表明具體會做甚麼來兌現承諾。<br />\n<br />\n最後一場辯論的六項議題，不包括外交政策，但兩人的對華立場仍然可從辯論國安等議題時，看出拜登擺出強硬姿態。<br />\n<br />\n拜登：「我會令中國遵守國際規則，不像特朗普所做的。我們已確認要在中國做生意，你要交出所有知識產權，並跟人合夥，而中國要佔比51%，我們絕不會這樣做。」<br />\n<br />\n拜登：「我在任副總統跟習近平會面時，他說『我們正在南海設立防空識別區，你們不能飛越那些空域。』我說我們會飛越它們，我們剛派出B-52和B-1轟炸機到那裡。我們不會理會，他們必須遵守規則，特朗普做過甚麼？他擁抱暴徒，像北韓、中國國家主席和（俄羅斯總統）普京等。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普曾誓言中國必須為新冠病毒蔓延全球付出巨大代價，當主持人追問他實質會做甚麼迫使中國負責，他提到貿易戰已令中國付出沉重代價。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普：「（你說過要讓他們付出代價）首先，中國已在付出代價。他們正支付數以十億美元，我才剛把280億美元...（新制裁？）我才剛把280億美元給予我們的農民。（那是納稅人的錢）甚麼？（納稅人的錢，不是來自中國）你知道納稅人是誰，它叫中國。」<br />\n<br />\n中國、俄羅斯和伊朗都被指試圖影響美國大選，拜登表明一旦當選，任何干預美國選舉的國家都要付出代價。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普被問到如果成功連任會如何處理這個問題時，則把話題轉移到拜登兒子涉及烏克蘭的利益輸送醜聞。"},{"pid":"8eb066b7e18e3f653bba038776b36803a9735b8a","tid":2429550,"uid":46161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:33:19.000Z","msg":"Er........"},{"pid":"cadfe1045f5aa0f2cd9576225caef4102de930cf","tid":2429550,"uid":266503,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jQowssL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjQowssL.gif&h=91272cf6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7857bb75f7b439baa42dcdb599589c0c3d1643d9","tid":2429550,"uid":214502,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:35:14.000Z","msg":"方法係...唔記得左!"},{"pid":"5f7c76ac81e24340e423948e2fecf74bcc6b970f","tid":2429550,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:36:49.000Z","msg":"All talk<br />\nno action<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214f285c7cd83af12b6d10409099dc45a6b64732","tid":2429550,"uid":370061,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:36:55.000Z","msg":"方法是讓中國創造新的國際規則<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914de3e7a635f9cb64f8f8671d615cc60339f2f4","tid":2429550,"uid":366655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:37:51.000Z","msg":"幼幼外交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7254d8503d7316913351d792a6cf33ed9ab42757","tid":2429550,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"敖清又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88718a2a8b0e3b0968997ab181f35bd9e9fc47b","tid":2429550,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:41:17.000Z","msg":"講漏咗，遵守中國制定的國際規則<br />\n例如人權包括國家自身發展權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa913c9d05ec4a04d1e7eeeb2cfc9c50a7663436","tid":2429550,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:41:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5X0Cn3s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5X0Cn3s.gif&h=e15eec18&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfbb3b41d1518546c86d71f1ee977a5e63bd0e11","tid":2429550,"uid":335783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"國際線左膠岀黎解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又話呀祖反共嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44f1fde4108ecc24538f14fe13828fbc5ca52cc","tid":2429550,"uid":8308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T